{"tid":2352494,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司每日都好好咁請我哋啲員工食屎","createTime":"2021-01-04T05:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T13:18:34.000Z","uid":369031,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"49da2a3b860db2109386fe549b963d0c2ccf4806","tid":2352494,"uid":369031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的 唔知你哋公司係咪咁樣 <br />\n我哋老細每日都會喺飯商訂啲飯俾員工免費食<br />\n但我想講 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">真係好撚難食啊屌！！！</span></span><br />\n但其他啲老屎忽唔知係咪食慣屎 竟然仲讚啲嘢食好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出去食個飯又好撚貴 唯有每日繼續留喺office食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4c6484cba872617492e2f55ee489baef3e18d7","tid":2352494,"uid":50660,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"包一餐仲想點？"},{"pid":"16e1b0f98b56c2a1c7ba76d5d28af09756870300","tid":2352494,"uid":77320,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"講得出出去食個飯都好貴就代表你淨係配食屎<br />\n完"},{"pid":"dafc5882c69d5845262ea7dbd7e6e19f751c8609","tid":2352494,"uid":70505,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:24:39.000Z","msg":"免費飯，你唔鍾意咪出去食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要比錢又難食個d先叫屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed0bb4f26a7507b9e99717be190a01a7675325d","tid":2352494,"uid":125380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"免費野想點"},{"pid":"adb4e4361c8851f9fd87c2bd04107e4ffe7b4f08","tid":2352494,"uid":8308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"office工?<br />\n包飯好撚正喎<br />\n利申 垃圾口 食得飽就得"},{"pid":"9f2b5c2e3c355de798e42c801f12d10f959a308a","tid":2352494,"uid":147629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"工你唔轉，連個飯都無能力買，咁都唔抵你食屎嘅話諗唔到有咩人抵過你食，班老屎忽唔係鐘意食，係唔想好似你咁可憐所以催眠自己啲飯好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20357e2fb7706976272573139e4c8be5bfed619c","tid":2352494,"uid":78856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"樓主做庇護工場？"},{"pid":"d51962575b9988dfdef16f1083f542a9477136ea","tid":2352494,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"唔好鬧樓主<br />\n<br />\n大種乞衣係咁諗野<br />\n<br />\n明哥飯盒「三文魚塊腥臭」、「天天都是肉餅」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2347369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2347369</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3bdb088fd7ecc1a59f4ad1b96e10e9e3a51b023","tid":2352494,"uid":35315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"出去食個飯又好撚貴<br />\n<br />\n咁你真係只係岩食屎"},{"pid":"74158dc4e2ab379ff76860dde5d6a786c9379dbd","tid":2352494,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20357e2fb7706976272573139e4c8be5bfed619c","tid":2352494,"uid":78856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"樓主做庇護工場？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d9beed694de5af1862ceb7cdbf88668ee69e95","tid":2352494,"uid":53209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T12:57:51.000Z","msg":"on9 公司包飯 你仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個個月洗少幾多錢"},{"pid":"9600e560654ef75d9dc805fc7d4d989ce72ab723","tid":2352494,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"難食咪拎去餵狗,自己另外買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}